 on the servers. Encryption helps keep the contents of your files from hackers who gain access to the remote servers. In addition, to keep the servers safe from unwanted external and internal attacks, Box uses firewalls and virus scanners. You also have the option to protect the URL links that you create with passwords so that only the intended recipient sees the files.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/54539-box3.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/z6mczcrKqR7QJqyDovqp7S.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"z6mczcrKqR7QJqyDovqp7S","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/z6mczcrKqR7QJqyDovqp7S.jpg","alt":""},"id":"a47a3fc6-936e-4b12-acad-5ccc0f688c50","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["One of the best security features that you get with Box is the remote wipe tool. This option allows you to remove files from any computer attached to your account. If you have multiple employees, clients or other users on your account, a remote wipe option is vital to ensuring that your files remain within your control when someone leaves the account. For example, if an employee leaves the company, you can delete all of the files associated with your Box account from the employee&#39;s computer, and you can do this from any web browser. In addition, this tool protects your files if one of your devices is stolen."]},"id":"4a088790-6142-495b-8f59-7fc5952a7b73","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"File Tracking Controls"},"id":"1c96d39b-826c-448d-bd3d-a47acc4b2ba7","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/2D2LJ394KnXC4hsJUdUnPG.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Box&#39;s file-tracking features give you full control over how you share and edit files within and without your account. The audit log, which is similar to a news feed on Facebook, details all of the file activity. This includes how many times you share a file, how you shared the file, with whom you shared it and when it was received. You can also track the ac